docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Cities): Middle Tier - Swansea, MA
docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of middle tier homes within the city of Swansea, MA. Middle tier homes are homes that fall into the middle third of home values within the region. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
